To create dashboards: Run Reports AND Create and Customize Dashboards
Create the custom reports containing the data you want to display.
Click the Dashboards tab.
Click Go To Dashboard List.
Click New Dashboard.
Customize your dashboard and click Save.
Salesforce Classic Dashboards
A dashboard shows data from source reports as visual components, which can be charts, gauges, tables, metrics, or Visualforce pages.
Edit Dashboards in Accessibility Mode in Salesforce Classic
Delete a Dashboard
